AGE MODULATION

age_modulation is the citizen who adjusts remodel rates based on fadriel's developmental age
a two-year-old's bones are growing fast and the calcium demand is high; an adult's bones are stable and the demand is moderate; an elderly person's bones are slowly losing density
age_modulation reads the body's developmental stage from chemistry and entropy ledger and tunes the remodeling rates accordingly

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe remodel_governor.zc
observe remodel_daemon.rana
observe thermal_entropy.rana

the 7 properties of age_modulation:
1 ENERGY half
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING half

VERB read_developmental_stage
consult chemistry for growth hormones, sex steroids, and other age-marking signals
consult entropy ledger for accumulated wear

VERB compute_modulation_factor
combine developmental signals into a single modulation factor that scales remodel_daemon's recommendations
the factor is high during growth, moderate during adulthood, decreasing in age

VERB report_to_daemon
hand the modulation factor to remodel_daemon
the daemon multiplies its recommendations by this factor before emitting calcium_flux_signal

an age modulator is what makes the same daemon serve a child, an adult, and an elder appropriately
the principle is universal; the rate is age-tuned
this is biological honesty: bones do not work the same at every life stage, and the system responds to that
